{"tid":2364830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"莊思明楊明抗疫湯店再開分舖：飲到屋企味","createTime":"2021-01-13T09:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T12:53:54.000Z","uid":128369,"like":16,"dislike":600,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4d73ed49879370a18dd7f817d7c56d562c9a41","tid":2364830,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"藝人莊思明、楊明的燉湯店於太子開設第6間分店，好友曹永廉、姚瑩瑩等出席開幕禮奌上祝賀。思明接受東網訪問時說：「我哋好感恩，依家係逆巿，疫情都未好穩定，我哋都可以開到分店，好多謝客人一直咁支持我哋，平時見到啲街坊，佢哋都話好鍾意飲我哋嘅湯，食我哋嘅嘢，話有屋企嘅味道，我都期望生意生意愈做愈好，最期待嘅係可以每一區都有分店。」<br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEeBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=6986f10f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>"},{"pid":"2835215501428a3b28830432ba9c5574a6b5e6b5","tid":2364830,"uid":70439,"like":315,"dislike":6,"score":309,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"藍絲果然食開屎飲開尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895909083a34e2139d5beb65206b41fc16a5d240","tid":2364830,"uid":38904,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"代表業主多謝佢哋炒高舖價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01eca212b7aecaccabe32d880542c5c111754af7","tid":2364830,"uid":12991,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"咪又係駛條女錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dccf4048e01a2657e495f76ba54e87cedc29461","tid":2364830,"uid":361751,"like":15,"dislike":46,"score":-31,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"龍門就執剩幾間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b3ba4a330e639437b5e8f10bc25fa7d414062f","tid":2364830,"uid":34410,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cl